{"tid":670792,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有心事嘅入嚟擺低 冇心事嘅入嚟吹水 (184)","createTime":"2018-05-19T16:11:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-20T07:54:19.000Z","uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c4d5201c694fecac8d5b9224a938e51903089106","tid":670792,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T16:11:11.000Z","msg":"唔小心一百八十四咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n繼續有心事入嚟擺低 無心事入嚟吹水<br />\n絕非小圈子 有心事就算見到吹緊水都唔使怕羞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時候有啲巴絲比既意見會比較直擊 大家唔好嚇親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時有啲巴絲講野好低b 因為都係無聊野傾到冇野傾先講低b嘢<br />\n所以好歡迎新話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時候有啲巴絲會po啲好黑既嘢<br />\n又有時候會無啦啦變左成人台<br />\n如果你handle唔到可以唔理佢地<br />\nhandle唔到都無辦法啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望多啲人討論歌詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋遷就唔識英文同日文嘅巴絲 唔該<br />\n<br />\n如果見到有啲reply覺得唔係太舒服 請體諒呢個po大多都係有心事有情緒既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請1001 嘅巴絲開post<br />\n<br />\n希望大家開心啲同早啲訓教<br />\n<br />\n請詩記得食🍊<br />\n請蕃茄妹記得早啲瞓覺"},{"pid":"30ef246902542cad5f865b3326c11bb5438eb639","tid":670792,"uid":145117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T16:12:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fb9052970810cf91489258469c591bc69b487dc","tid":670792,"uid":124256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T07:42:01.000Z","msg":"hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1633b0136434910582b18b67b2b3add597c42670","tid":670792,"uid":6744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T07:54:19.000Z","msg":"回到以前~~~~"}]}